{"word":"κρήμνημι","slug":"κρήμνημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κρήμνημι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:κρεμάννυμι'><el>κρεμάννυμι</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>\n<p/><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <el>κρήμναμαι</el>, <i>to hang, be suspended</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <i>to float in air</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}